i\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T17:17:09.000Z","msg":"極懷疑條廢老講大話<br />\nD口供不斷彈出又彈入"},{"pid":"57ebab6e6dae1bf6534e7d9766757fb1091be8e7","tid":1856573,"uid":275865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T17:17:26.000Z","msg":"話唔定係隻船<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fd8890ed9377b5ced6bb2a95e7e65ed186a6e12","tid":1856573,"uid":301152,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"5c87a0f96eadc37e3b9fc6d43bd40af850e8c49d","tid":1856573,"uid":24660,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"quote":{"pid":"ad233584678582a0c873a17b6e6195f73a64dec8","tid":1856573,"uid":49316,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"e4e6ff0f965f4f4db5d251ea87e7e51a5e5b9b7c","tid":1856573,"uid":161374,"like":85,"dislike":1,"score":84,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T16:50:36.000Z","msg":"咁其實船上有中國人都唔定<br />\n船都幾危險"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T16:56:25.000Z","msg":"十九才子之前唔係坐郵輪<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T16:59:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n上郵輪之前，要做功課，了解乘客成份。「鑽石公主」號以日本中產為主，西洋客若干，香港遊客少量，見此Profiling，可知文明指數有保障，噪音在可控範圍，放下心頭大石。<br />\n<br />\n東京去鹿兒島，航程竟要兩日。船上食物，由日本供應，牛肉豚肉都勝過歐洲航線。一出公海，網絡訊號消失，武肺的訊息，連同那許多呼天搶地的恐慌喧嘩，通通都不見了。<br />\n<br />\n見不到，聽不見，不就等同不存在了嗎？「鑽石公主」號在暮色中航行。沒有手提電話，原來日子是如此的潔淨太平、寧靜美好。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E9%99%B6%E5%82%91/daily/article/20200123/20848552/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E9%2599%25B6%25E5%2582%2591%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20200123%2F20848552%2F&d=ANzGKs6Ysw%2B%2BKy1wioRXtzk5r7V16zLonem%2BWgH46Yg%3D&h=9941b31e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E9%2599%25B6%25E5%2582%2591%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20200123%2F20848552%2F&h=81724d1f\" target=\"_blank\