article/20200123/20848552/</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T17:52:29.000Z","msg":"寫完即刻出事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />?"},{"pid":"647a9b39ef0c46a6e1300b1ef08c2f3f4e2fa4e4","tid":1856573,"uid":277009,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6ad36df17e601eb91373e2e4912cd3956733dba7","tid":1856573,"uid":63154,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T16:59:47.000Z","msg":"假設佢10號中招，19號先咳，30號先發燒？要成20日？應該冇咁耐掛"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T18:01:27.000Z","msg":"人地成八十歲，有幾聲咳唔代表乜嘢嘅"},{"pid":"bc1f8308f168ff139307091896bd0603f42ecbd4","tid":1856573,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T18:06:02.000Z","msg":"80歲仲到處跑<br />\n去深圳肯定叫雞"},{"pid":"d6847d11d379421f3b1a43bb69b38a5252778276","tid":1856573,"uid":301152,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c4edf411cd84912cb287a6b036a4e8b9b40d65c1","tid":1856573,"uid":62935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5c87a0f96eadc37e3b9fc6d43bd40af850e8c49d","tid":1856573,"uid":24660,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"quote":{"pid":"ad233584678582a0c873a17b6e6195f73a64dec8","tid":1856573,"uid":49316,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T16:56:25.000Z","msg":"十九才子之前唔係坐郵輪<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T16:59:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n上郵輪之前，要做功課，了解乘客成份。「鑽石公主」號以日本中產為主，西洋客若干，香港遊客少量，見此Profiling，可知文明指數有保障，噪音在可控範圍，放下心頭大石。<br />\n<br />\n東京去鹿兒島，航程竟要兩日。船上食物，由日本供應，牛肉豚肉都勝過歐洲航線。一出公海，網絡訊號消失，武肺的訊息，連同那許多呼天搶地的恐慌喧嘩，通通都不見了。<br />\n<br />\n見不到，聽不見，不就等同不存在了嗎？「鑽石公主」號在暮色中航行。沒有手提電話，原來日子是如此的潔淨太平、寧靜美好。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E9%99%B6%E5%82%91/daily/article/20200123/20848552/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E9%2599%25B6%25E5%2582%