209390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T18:53:03.000Z","msg":"30號先燒 我反而覺得佢係遊輪惹返黎<br />\nBtw 19<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2017c6d35b403c2411d3bdc818a826cdead864d6","tid":1856573,"uid":63311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"38b6f71525aae2f3c0361ec2473adab46ccf387b","tid":1856573,"uid":193538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T18:38:54.000Z","msg":"diu , 我住呢條村, 死癈老<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T18:54:06.000Z","msg":"成棟樓消毒"},{"pid":"e32d147ce0f870bf74f987ac9a2f26273daf21f5","tid":1856573,"uid":55533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cb31d1d71b3814dd1ae43dc224be6186b3ee1f5b","tid":1856573,"uid":1251,"like":29,"dislike":1,"score":28,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T16:52:13.000Z","msg":"好人好姐返乜野大陸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />累死人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T18:58:25.000Z","msg":"藍屍最鐘意進出支那<br />\n食水煮地溝油孔雀石綠魚飲化學茶行大商場"},{"pid":"33f68b798d31323b0e4c31eb4a2025d0f50f1ffb","tid":1856573,"uid":55533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T19:00:33.000Z","msg":"郵輪最撚污糟<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f0ed1ccc6c5324750f81bcadd6f36ae1d3488d7","tid":1856573,"uid":59617,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T19:03:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://today.line.me/HK/article/JWnYMM?utm_source=copyshare\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftoday.line.me%2FHK%2Farticle%2FJWnYMM%3Futm_source%3Dcopyshare&d=ANzGKs6Ysw%2B%2BKy1wioRXtzk5r7V16zLonem%2BWgH46Yg%3D&h=702e074b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://today.line.me/HK/article/JWnYMM?utm_source=copyshare</a><br />\n大陸老婆<br />\n據醫護人員向《立場新聞》透露，該名80歲的男病人求醫時報稱曾乘遊輪到日本，途中沒有經過中國、台灣、韓國的城市，只是到過日本鹿兒島；返港後持續一個星期咳嗽及發燒。男病人重覆強調自己沒有去過中國，而他女兒卻有上呼吸道感染徵狀。男病人的妻子沒有上郵輪，但當護士問及太太電話時，對方給予一個內地號碼。<br />\n<br />\n消息人士形容「幸好」護士覺得可疑，所以決定把他送往隔離病房，而由於內科病房爆滿，他被送到外科病房隔離。不過男子曾在上月 15 日到過聯合醫院骨科覆診，另外他在明愛轉院往瑪嘉烈時一度逃走，但救護車剛剛駛至，男子被監護下送往瑪嘉烈醫院就醫。男子初步診斷發現，其肺片左上部同右下部有花，肝功能不正常。"}]}